# AI Workflow

## Step 1

User sends prompt.

## Step 2

Conversation history is loaded.

## Step 3

Memory engine retrieves relevant context.

## Step 4

Prompt is enhanced using retrieved memories.

## Step 5

Prompt is sent to Mistral 7B.

## Step 6

Model generates response.

## Step 7

Response is streamed to frontend.

## Step 8

Conversation is stored.

## Step 9

Embeddings are created.

## Step 10

Memory database is updated.

